Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:27.97,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Aimerais-tu, en ce monde, voir quelque chose s'effacer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:35.16,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Et que l'air soit plus pur, le coeur des hommes transformé
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:42.01,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Et pourtant, tout est si fragile ici, sur la Terre
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:48.46,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Il n'est rien qui soit futile, tu sais
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:06.59,French,,0000,0000,0000,,D'un coté beau ou bon et quelquefois prodigieux
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:13.87,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Et de l'autre laid ou pauvre et bien souvent monstrueux
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:20.72,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Qu'importe ce que ton coeur te dictera, souviens-toi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:26.95,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Que la différence naît dans tes yeux
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:35.11,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Chante toutes les couleurs du Monde
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:42.35,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Sans manquer une seule note
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:48.39,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaque chose a sa place ici
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:58.70,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaque émoi forme la symphonie de notre vie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:10.32,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Savoure l'harmonie du ciel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:17.68,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Vois que tout est essentiel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:30.98,French,,0000,0000,0000,,Et comprends que, toi aussi, tu en écris la mélodie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:27.97,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to see something, in this world, erase itself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:35.16,English,,0000,0000,0000,,And the air be purer, the hearts of men transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:42.01,English,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet everything is so fragile here, on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:48.46,English,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that is futile, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:06.59,English,,0000,0000,0000,,From one side beautiful or good, and sometimes prodigious
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:13.87,English,,0000,0000,0000,,And from the other ugly or poor, and often monstrous
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:20.72,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever your heart dictates to you, remember
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:26.95,English,,0000,0000,0000,,That the difference is born in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:35.11,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing all the colours of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:42.35,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Without missing a single note
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:48.39,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has its place here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:58.70,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Every excitement forms the symphony of our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:10.32,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Savour the harmony of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:17.68,English,,0000,0000,0000,,See that everything is essential
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:30.98,English,,0000,0000,0000,,And understand that, you too, you write the melody
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:44.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:53.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are going to Mistran?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you offend anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:59.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well it's a place with a lot of delicious food and beautiful girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been half a year since the cease-fire started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:05.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the survivors from the war that are the winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Clim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:12.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lucky, Captain Tamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:13.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:16.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake now, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:19.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our loot, please take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:23.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:28.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's really an honour to receive such a precious gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:37.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you that if you have a good relationship with the bugler, you will not miss the retreating bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:40.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The drafting has stopped. Trainees should be rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:42.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want to learn music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What???
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:48.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:53.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to be honest, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:55.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Private, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:56.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:51.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,112.5)}Resounding Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:51.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,651.25)}The City at Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a festival in Seize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I have to stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you're assigned to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it the "Time telling fortress."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Find your way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Appointment document.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami Kanata,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:41.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Effective immediately, you are assigned to Platoon 1121 of Seize, Trois Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Army Headquarter of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Task Completed at 13:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:14.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of lakes and glass, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Report time is 15:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I will let you show your nice sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Direction check. Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Time check. Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment check. Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:20.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat.  What a wonderful sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...A fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10 Yen 25 Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful, this doll ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A little cat lost in the festive atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:48.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's heading towards somewhere she doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Small cats always love to wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they are lovely. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You would have been right, if it were a wild cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:05.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, that is a tamed cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really frightened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have found another nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:47.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Soldier-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl from the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth celebrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the flame, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:53.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all wet! Are you going to report in this uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A...Actually...Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank yo-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...That's enough. Come along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the water temperature okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:42.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you are a target that everyone loves to shoot at. Can't you try to evade?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:47.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy. This dye will fade after drying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is that the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It originated from a local tale of Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A tale? What is it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:04.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of Flame, protecting the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry for all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:20.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be billed. The repair is already done as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And also there's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really a busybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.80,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So late.  So late. She's really late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I deliberately came out to welcome her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:45.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My, just be patient and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.48,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from your father, right? It is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:54.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:03.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I don't know why I always get easily lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is really my pleasure to meet nice people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But please don't get lost here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow! Ha Ha Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can distinguish pitches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:37.69,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A clear and melodious sound, and it's nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I don't really mean this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:43.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:53.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you forget about your life for that kind of thing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:06.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, let it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:18.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.92,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do so I am leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:40.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell must be very precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of Flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:11.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Way before the world became like the one we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:18.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the bottom of the valley in this city, there was a demon living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:28.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon breathed fire, and shook the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People were living in hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:37.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And one day, it kidnapped the maidens who lived in the fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and imprisoned them in an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the maidens didn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:59.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sounded the gold horn bestowed by the angels to escape from the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By borrowing the enormous power from the spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They knocked down the demon, and cut its head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:13.00,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the heads started breathing out fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:17.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this kept on, the town above would be engulfed by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:25.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent the fire from spreading outside, the maidens held the demon's head one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:32.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People splashed water at the demon's head and the maidens,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.40,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fire was finally extinguished after a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:41.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, to worship the maidens who sacrificed their lives to save the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Water Festival was started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come after all... that newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.63,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, captain! Rio-senpai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. It suits her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting her perform the ritual is the righteous choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:55.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it decided by drawing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also fun when I'm lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:28.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because I meet new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:34.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone... I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:40.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I want my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings will be felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:49.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.29,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound will surely reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...surely reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:06.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of Flame, we bless your rest peacefully
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Clench the demon. Relieve the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:15.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray that the day of the demon's awakening never comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:16.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden horn!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the awakening of the demon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:38.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May it.. reach someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:59.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:15.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.70,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you still want to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, is the Time telling fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The station of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:42.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday... well... I am sorry for the trouble I caused!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:44.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, it was troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.11,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.03,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, don't be reckless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:55.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's reckless to do such things just for this bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.56,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why this fortress is called the "Time telling fortress".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Sound of the Skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:41.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:46.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to teach you how to become a trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:50.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of me, Staff Sergeant Rio-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:51.98,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:59.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the captain's decision. We don't use military rank here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:00.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:03.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:03.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:08.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, shall we start now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Reveille. Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:30.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is really bad at it...
